{"tid":334210,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"公佈LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃附加賽最後一圈對賽詳情","createTime":"2017-07-24T13:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T19:16:13.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22dc870431711baee378fc99aa096357957c74ac","tid":334210,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T13:34:01.000Z","msg":"經過一連數星期既地區決定賽較量之後,關乎最後4個分組賽名額花落誰家既附加賽最後一圈既對賽組合終於有結果啦,密切留意以下比賽日期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃附加賽首回合(附加賽兩回合勝方將獲最後四席分組賽名額)*<br />\n2017-7-30 12am-10pm<br />\n12:00am 平井桃@TWICE vs 宋智孝<br />\n12:02am 田馥甄 vs 陳穎欣@SG<br />\n12:04am 林詩枝 vs 劉亦菲<br />\n12:06am Blake Lively vs M&eacute;lanie Laurent<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃附加賽次回合(附加賽兩回合勝方將獲最後四席分組賽名額)*<br />\n2017-8-5 12am-10pm<br />\n12:00am 宋智孝 vs 平井桃@TWICE<br />\n12:02am 陳穎欣@SG vs 田馥甄<br />\n12:04am 劉亦菲 vs 林詩枝<br />\n12:06am M&eacute;lanie Laurent vs Blake Lively<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10715241be1fa3a8dd002ffe5448ba44d45c6e4d","tid":334210,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T13:34:18.000Z","msg":"以下為已經晉身分組賽階段之女神名單:<br />\n<br />\n第一種子(POT1):<br />\n朱千雪(香港)、Emma Watson(英國)、Elizabeth Olsen(美國)、新垣結衣(日本)、林娜璉@TWICE(韓國)、唐嫣(中國)、周子瑜(台灣)、林明禎(馬來西亞)<br />\n<br />\n第二種子(POT2):<br />\n謝安琪(香港)、李佳芯(香港)、名井南@TWICE(日本)、長澤正美(日本)、IU(韓國)、金所炫(韓國)、林宣妤(馬來西亞)、Jennifer Lawrence(美國)<br />\n<br />\n第三種子(POT3):<br />\n楊丞琳(台灣)、Emma Stone(美國)、Natalie Portman(以色列)、Gal Gadot(以色列)、Saoirse Ronan(愛爾蘭)、Rachel McAdams(加拿大)、Ellen Page(加拿大)、Beer Passaranan(泰國)<br />\n<br />\n第四種子(POT4):<br />\nKeira Knightley(英國)、Margot Robbie(澳洲)、朱主愛(馬來西亞)、Candice Swanepoel(南非)、平井桃@TWICE(日本)或宋智孝(韓國)、田馥甄(台灣)或陳穎欣@SG(香港)、林詩枝(馬來西亞)或劉亦菲(中國)、Blake Lively(美國)或M&eacute;lanie Laurent(法國)<br />\n<br />\n再次提醒大家,餘下分組賽席位將通過8大區附加賽決出<br />\n日本:平井桃@TWICE 對 韓國:宋智孝<br />\n台灣:田馥甄 對 香港:陳穎欣@SG<br />\n其他地區:林詩枝(馬來西亞) 對 中國:劉亦菲<br />\n美國:Blake Lively 對 歐洲:M&eacute;lanie Laurent(法國)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783d590124ea74b0bc7da5cab730d8171a7ecbb1","tid":334210,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T21:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be3cd122bc3e1876c08dba63acf6ecbda3f6e50","tid":334210,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T03:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9e0ae1768d94bdf797beeb7a08076134f3c735","tid":334210,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da7769f051c962dc481007fe60139028c0068a6","tid":334210,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T19:19:16.000Z","msg":"留意返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2862ea903e845552aed3f188831c84a2eca110","tid":334210,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T16:09:43.000Z","msg":"開始左啦喂,比賽post呢度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/340134\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/340134</a>"},{"pid":"ae76ecd7968ebe69bab59e4ebde54fdff729f5c6","tid":334210,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"首回合戰果<br />\n<br />\n平井桃@TWICE 57-44 宋智孝<br />\n田馥甄 32-49 陳穎欣@SG<br />\n林詩枝 47-32 劉亦菲<br />\nBlake Lively 41-10 M&eacute;lanie Laurent<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/b